1-No Authentication
2-The Template files and database files are in DocumentRoot
3-The database in plain text
4-No field validation enforced, so the app is vulnerable to SQL injection/XSS attacks
5-Not a user friendly
6-There is no main menu page
7-No Insert
8-No Delete
9-Some parts are repeated such as getting invoice by id (qi and qq)
10-Not all errors are handeld
11-No event logger has been implemented.
